{"tid":992450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為呃 like 老屈大叔藏偷拍鏡頭 醒目網民踢爆是\"改圖\"","createTime":"2019-01-23T07:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T22:09:23.000Z","uid":59952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"09477abbc4b3950e48ca2dfa9ff06abd1b41666c","tid":992450,"uid":59952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2255000/2257428/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2255000%2F2257428%2F2_1024.jpg&h=7f4c1cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在這個網絡世界，不少人都想出位成名，有時甚至會不擇手段。早前在日本，一位女網民便在 Twitter 分享了一張相片，指坐電車時看到一名大叔，將鏡頭藏在大腿之間用來偷拍，成功引來大量網民分享及讚好。不過當中亦有心水清的網民，放大圖片分析，最後發現鏡頭是用軟件後製加上去。簡單點說，就是該女網民疑似想走紅，於是誣蔑一位陌生大叔是痴漢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2255000/2257428/3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2255000%2F2257428%2F3_600.jpg&h=91489d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該名女網民被踢爆後，先是封鎖分析者，然後再刪帖，嘗試推卸責任，可以仍擋不住眾怒，最後唯刪除 Twitter 帳戶敗走，事件似乎只能石沉大海。至於網民的留言則包括：「在日本這可是很嚴重的指控啊，還好有被人發現，不然大叔應該死定了」、「男生真的要好好保護自己」、「如何讓一名無辜的男人在社會上受到最嚴厲的指責甚至被抺除？告他性侵」、「真的要偷拍會放在這麼容易發現的地方嗎」等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2254201/%E3%80%904000%E8%9A%8A%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90%E3%80%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B4%BE%20%EF%BC%844000%20%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%98%E6%AD%A5%E9%A9%9F%E5%8F%8A%E5%A1%AB%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%8C%E4%BC%8F%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2254201%2F%25E3%2580%25904000%25E8%259A%258A%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B5%2590%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B4%25BE%2520%25EF%25BC%25844000%2520%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E9%25A0%2598%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E9%25A9%259F%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25BC%258F%25E4%25BD%258D%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%25A0%2585&d=IoclT1kYyzcwpF8g0EMZp26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b878c7ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2254201/%E3%80%904000%E8%9A%8A%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90%E3%80%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B4%BE%20%EF%BC%844000%20%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%98%E6%AD%A5%E9%A9%9F%E5%8F%8A%E5%A1%AB%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%8C%E4%BC%8F%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85</a>"},{"pid":"2e3f57a212dffe9bac48ed0e44d11df63c3eed96","tid":992450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，出post時出錯source,應該係呢個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2257428/為呃%20like%20老屈大叔藏偷拍鏡頭%20醒目網民踢爆是%20P%20圖\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2257428%2F%E7%82%BA%E5%91%83%2520like%2520%E8%80%81%E5%B1%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94%E8%97%8F%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%2520%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E6%98%AF%2520P%2520%E5%9C%96&d=IoclT1kYyzcwpF8g0EMZp26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d59533ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2257428/為呃%20like%20老屈大叔藏偷拍鏡頭%20醒目網民踢爆是%20P%20圖</a><br />\n<br />\n順便多謝有人幫我代出post"},{"pid":"2409820cd2134a5dbfbd5dfe630149b4d0822220","tid":992450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990c6c6590ced8cfb6b41b37b7e2e80f0a007e6b","tid":992450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmo